nodes.text: The Strikefast was a Victory-class Star Destroyer of the Imperial Starfleet.

Its first appearance was in the Outer Rim Territories, under the command of Voss Parck. The vessel was chasing Booster Terrik when it came upon a world where a local inhabitant destroyed the landing party's TIEs and shuttles using the native flora and fauna. Impressed, Parck took the alien—Mitth'raw'nuruodo—back to the Galactic Empire.
